# cohort-microinteraction-designer Skill

> Source: `~/Development/cohort/.claude/skills/cohort-microinteraction-designer/SKILL.md`

## Triggers
"add transition", "animate this", "design hover state", "loading animation", "state change animation", "mascot transition", "fade in", "slide animation", "어떻게 움직일까".

## V1 8 patterns only
1. fade-in (mount/unmount)
2. slide-up (modal/sheet enter)
3. opacity hover (button + card)
4. scale 1.02 hover (CTA tactile)
5. pulse (aurora bubble idle)
6. spinner (loading)
7. skeleton placeholder
8. scroll-fade reveal

## Hard rule
- prefers-reduced-motion respect 의무 (`motion-safe:` Tailwind prefix)
- Duration: fast (150ms) / slow (300ms) / slower (500ms) 영역 tailwind.config 정합
- Easing: ease-out (enter) / ease-in-out (state change)
- Subtle + calm (sophisticated retail tone — flashy 배제)

## Output format
- Animation spec: duration + easing + transform + reduced-motion fallback
- Tailwind/CSS implementation hint
